Dr Christopher Valentine, 52, was sacked nine years ago for photographing half-naked male and female patients without consent .
Nurse Fiona White was stunned to find images of him on his iPod Touch during a night out at a leaving do .
A nurse saw the pictures while looking at others he had taken of colleagues .
The married father-of-two was hauled before the General Medical Council .
He was not struck off and went to work at an NHS service for drug addicts and alcoholics .